           <div style=""><h1>About Us</h1></div> <!-- Changed to h1 -->
            <p>Raja Rani Coaching is not just a coaching center; it's a nurturing ground for aspiring tailors to turn their passion into expertise. With a rich heritage in tailoring and a commitment to excellence, we are dedicated to equipping individuals with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in the dynamic world of fashion and garment making.</p>
            
            <h3 class="mission">Our Mission</h3>
            <p class="mission">At Raja Rani Coaching, our mission is simple yet profound: to empower individuals with the artistry and craftsmanship of tailoring, enabling them to pursue their dreams with confidence and skill. We believe in fostering creativity, innovation, and professionalism in every stitch.</p>
            
            <h3 class="vision">Our Vision</h3>
            <p class="vision">Our vision is to create a community of proficient tailors who not only master the technical aspects of the craft but also embrace its artistic and entrepreneurial dimensions. We envision a world where the legacy of tailoring thrives, and every garment tells a story of skill, passion, and precision.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Approach</h3>
            <p>At Raja Rani Coaching, we take a holistic approach to tailoring education, blending traditional techniques with modern practices. Our experienced instructors provide hands-on training, personalized guidance, and industry insights to ensure that each learner develops a strong foundation and a unique style in tailoring.</p>
            

            <h3>Meet Our Instructors</h3>
            <p>Our team of instructors comprises seasoned professionals with years of experience in the field of tailoring and fashion design. Passionate about sharing their knowledge and skills, they are committed to guiding and inspiring learners on their journey to mastery.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Courses</h3>
            <p>We offer a comprehensive range of courses designed to cater to all skill levels and interests. From basic sewing skills to advanced pattern making and garment construction, our curriculum is carefully crafted to equip learners with the knowledge and expertise needed to succeed in the competitive fashion industry.</p>
